This plugin provides 3D visualization capabilities for images and meshes using the [https://github.com/ClearVolume/scenery Scenery] and [[ClearVolume]] infrastructure. An ambition of this plugin is to serve as a modern replacement to [[3D Viewer]]. SciView also integrates [[ImageJ2]] functionality, including [[ImageJ Ops]].
